data.name: GetInsuranceCompany
data.value: Select InsuranceCompanyId, DistrictId, InsuranceCompany, AddressLine1, CountryHead from [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceCompany] where DeletedDate is null

data.name: GetInsuranceCompanybyId
data.value: Select DistrictId, InsuranceCompany, AddressLine1, CountryHead from [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceCompany] where DeletedDate is null and InsuranceCompanyId = @insuranceCompanyId

data.name: InsertInsuranceCompany
data.value: Insert into [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceCompany] (DistrictId, InsuranceCompany, AddressLine1, CountryHead, CreatedDate) values (@districtId, @insuranceCompany, @address, @countryHead, @createdDate)

data.name: UpdateInsuranceCompany
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceCompany] set DistrictId = @districtId, AddressLine1 = @address, InsuranceCompany = @insuranceCompany, CountryHead = @countryHead, ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate where InsuranceCompanyId = @insuranceCompanyId

data.name: GetInsuranceType
data.value: Select InsuranceTypeId, InsuranceType, InsuranceCompanyId from [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceType] where DeletedDate is null

data.name: GetInsuranceTypebyId
data.value: Select InsuranceType, InsuranceCompanyId from [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceType] where DeletedDate is null and InsuranceTypeId = @insuranceTypeId

data.name: UpdateInsuranceType
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceType] set ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate, InsuranceType = @insuranceType, InsuranceCompanyId = @insuranceCompanyId where InsuranceTypeId = @insuranceTypeId

data.name: GetInsuranceTypebyCompany
data.value: Select InsuranceType, InsuranceTypeId from [UnicoVehicle].[insurance].[InsuranceType] where DeletedDate is null and InsuranceCompanyId = @insuranceCompanyId
